  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CiviCRM
    This profile installs and configures CiviCRM (https://civicrm.org/) on a Drupal (7) base.
    Drupal7
    This profile will install and configure Drupal 7, and is kept only for legacy reasons.
    Drupal8
    This profile will install and configure Drupal 8
    DrupalCommons
    This profile install and configures Drupal Commons.
    Etherpad
    This profile creates and configures an Etherpad-Lite (https://github.com/ether/etherpad-lite) instance
    Grav

    This profile installs and configures a Horde installation

    This profile configures a MISP (https://www.misp-project.org/) server
